[Bakhshe 1]:
Sathe satro por mikonam ba ke baresh por beshe
Ba vazhehaye vagheio momtanee
Ke chon tan be tars dadam mikonm aghaz
Dastani rastan
Negargare avaze khan
Dar peye rang bakhshidan be sotast
Shako shekve ebdaa she to haste
Dur az zehn
Nist in khatm shebe ebtekar
Game nokhost ebteda:
Mosighiye bi omgh ba pahnaye bikhod
Darigh azyek hedayat
Sadegh rasekh ama fani enayat
Elat melat bahune ba revayat
Gelayeo kenayeo ghezavaat
Taghase kadret hishod ke
Nerkhe bomet gheychi shod?
Mokhtasate amvaje glitcham
Mokhtase signaa lasham  ke nistan
Faghato faghat marbote axa
Taraneye talkhe ghable margesh
Baade shera harbar
Paresham had nadare chon
Ja morakabam verd toye davateo
Davaye to hamine ke midam bekhordet
Ta sokhanano nagiri be sokhre

[Bakhshe 2]

Abyate roshan fekri kheyr vase samte feli
Eghdam be melke ghesdi seyre taze tahte teyfi
Teye tahdide Taye fe
Tarvije tarde rabete
Tandise talkhe jamee
Tasbite samte rakede
Pishman hamashun onaei ke to jeldaman
Jelveye raho hamishe bem neshun dadan eynaman
Agaram be khastam naresidam aa ro bi orzegiye khudame
Misazam zatame pey nabard
Bavaram baram bar aan su bud ama ozaa
Bar vefghe morade re ba ke
Zendegi chiginii var ba nono paniro araghe keshmeshiam berahe
Ruberahe

[Bakhshe 3]

Poshte dshkam
Bepsh ta bosh baz
Sar nagire mazeye demodegi mide dige josh nayomade
Be moghe tracket
Ter paket shode bazde nadare hich ghelzati
Salamgholi bemone tosh ba ezati
Ta sarf konam man game payanio enteharo ba ghesmti
Bishakk mishan takhaayolate sia ghalam varam eehya rango
Ehyanan na faghat shoaaro ezhar be adaa
Bishtar azinas